e;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h3>\n<p>시작하기 앞서 <code class=\"language-text\">커밋 타입</code>은 <code class=\"language-text\">feat</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">refactor</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">chore</code>와 같은 <a href=\"https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/\">Conventional Commits</a>의 <code class=\"language-text\">type</code>을 의미합니다.</p>\n<p>개발 환경은 다음과 같습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>MacOS 14.2.1(23C71)</li>\n<li>IntelliJ 2023.2.5 (Ultimate Edition)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"1-컨벤션-정하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EC%BB%A8%EB%B2%A4%EC%85%98-%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"1 컨벤션 정하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 컨벤션 정하기</h2>\n<p>해당 작업을 수행하기 전 <em>브랜치 네이밍 컨벤션</em> 과 <em>커밋 메시지 컨벤션</em> 을 먼저 정해야 합니다.</p>\n<p>이번 글에선 브랜치 네이밍 컨벤션을 <code class=\"language-text\">type/issue_number</code> 와 같은 형식으로, 커밋 메시지 컨벤션을 <code class=\"language-text\">type: message (#1)</code>와 같이 설정하겠습니다.<br></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>예) 브랜치 네이밍 컨벤션 : <code class=\"language-text\">feat/1</code><br>\n커밋 메시지 컨벤션 : <code class=\"language-text\">feat: 기능 구현 (#1)</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"2-스크립트-작성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8-%EC%9E%91%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"2 스크립트 작성 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 스크립트 작성</h2>\n<p>프로젝트의 루트 위치 아래에 <code class=\"language-text\">.githooks</code> 디렉터리를 만들고 그 안에 <code class=\"language-text\">commit-msg</code>를 만들어주세요.<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">commit-msg</code>는 단순히 file 형태로 만들면 됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 145px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d6c0e219475c6c3c3248bb5a297f1650/0af15/script_path.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.655172413793103%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"스크립트 경로\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d6c0e219475c6c3c3248bb5a297f1650/0af15/script_path.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d6c0e219475c6c3c3248bb5a297f1650/0af15/script_path.png 145w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 145px) 100vw, 145px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>그 다음 스크립트 코드를 작성하겠습니다.<br>\n코드에 대한 설명은 주석을 참고해주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token shebang important\">#!/bin/sh</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 본 스크립트는 브랜치 명을 토대로 개발자가 작성한 커밋 메시지에 자동으로 PREFIX와 POSTFIX 문자열을 추가하는 스크립트입니다.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 브랜치 명은 \"feat/14\" 와 같이 \"{type}/{issue_number}\" 의 형식입니다.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">COMMIT_MESSAGE_FILE_PATH</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\">$1</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 작성한 커밋 메시지가 저장된 File의 경로 추출</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">MESSAGE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">cat</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$COMMIT_MESSAGE_FILE_PATH</span>\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 작성한 커밋 메시지 추출</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 커밋 메시지가 존재하지 않은 경우, 스크립트 종료</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">head</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-1</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$COMMIT_MESSAGE_FILE_PATH</span>\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exit</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 브랜치 이름에서 '/' 이전의 문자열만 남긴다. 만약 명시적으로 type을 작성한 경우 작성하지 않는다.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$MESSAGE</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> *:* <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n  <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">PREFIX</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">git</span> branch <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\\*'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">'s/\\* //'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">'s/\\([^/]*\\).*/\\1/'</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>:\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 브랜치 이름에서 '/' 이후의 문자열만 남긴다. '/'가 없다면 브랜치 전체 이름이 POSTFIX가 된다.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># POSTFIX의 첫 번째 '-' 앞 뒤의 문자열만 포함한다. '-'가 없다면 변경은 없다.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 명시적으로 이슈 번호를 작성한 경우 작성하지 않는다.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$MESSAGE</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> *<span class=\"token comment\">#* ]]; then</span>\n  <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">POSTFIX</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"(#<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">git</span> branch <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\\*'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">'s/* //'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">'s/^.*\\///'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">'s/^\\([^-]*-[^-]*\\).*/\\1/'</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>)\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span>\n\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">printf</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"%s %s %s\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$PREFIX</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$MESSAGE</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$POSTFIX</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$COMMIT_MESSAGE_FILE_PATH</span>\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"3-git-hooks-설정-makefile-이용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-git-hooks-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-makefile-%EC%9D%B4%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"3 git hooks 설정 makefile 이용 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. git hooks 설정 (Makefile 이용)</h2>\n<p>git hooks를 설정해야 작성한 스크립트를 <strong>적용</strong>할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>설정하기 위한 명령어는 <code class=\"language-text\">git config core.hooksPath .githooks</code> 입니다.</p>\n<p>하지만 git hooks 설정 외에도 권한 관련 설정을 한번에 편하게 하기 위해 Mac(or Linux) OS에 기본적으로 제공되는 <a href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/make/\">Makefile</a>를 이용하겠습니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>프로젝트 루트 경로에 <code class=\"language-text\">Makefile</code>을 만들어줍니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 281px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4a26a31909d56dc73e0cb8d02dc085c7/6b1e2/Makefile.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 120.25316455696202%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Makefile 위치\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4a26a31909d56dc73e0cb8d02dc085c7/6b1e2/Makefile.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4a26a31909d56dc73e0cb8d02dc085c7/c26ae/Makefile.png 158w,\n/static/4a26a31909d56dc73e0cb8d02dc085c7/6b1e2/Makefile.png 281w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 281px) 100vw, 281px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Makefile에 아래의 코드를 작성합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">init:\n\t<span class=\"token function\">git</span> config core.hooksPath .githooks\n\t<span class=\"token function\">chmod</span> +x .githooks/commit-msg\n\t<span class=\"token function\">git</span> update-index <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--add</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--chmod</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>+x .githooks/commit-msg</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>Makefile 문법 상, 띄어쓰기가 아닌 Tab을 입력해야 합니다.<br></li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n코드 설명\n- `git config core.hooksPath .githooks`: git hooks의 위치를 .githooks로 변경합니다.<br>\n- `chmod +x .githooks/commit-msg`: ./githooks/commit-msg 파일을 실행할 권한을 부여합니다.<br>\n- `git update-index --add --chmod=+x .githooks/commit-msg`: git이 .githooks/commit-msg 파일을 실행할 권한을 부여합니다.\n</blockquote>\n<p>그 다음 터미널에서 <code class=\"language-text\">make</code> 명령어를 입력해 위 파일을 실행시켜줍니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 393px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e1941b3337350456ed6969947a79472a/d72ec/result_after_make.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 22.151898734177216%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"결과\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/e1941b3337350456ed6969947a79472a/d72ec/result_after_make.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e1941b3337350456ed6969947a79472a/c26ae/result_after_make.png 158w,\n/static/e1941b3337350456ed6969947a79472a/6bdcf/result_after_make.png 315w,\n/static/e1941b3337350456ed6969947a79472a/d72ec/result_after_make.png 393w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 393px) 100vw, 393px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"4-확인하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"4 확인하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. 확인하기</h2>\n<p>이제 끝났습니다.</p>\n<p>직접 커밋을 남겨보고 그 결과를 확인해보면 Prefix와 Postfix가 추가된 상태로 커밋되는 것을 확인할 수 있습니다!</p>\n<h2 id=\"주의사항-및-적용-해제하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9-%ED%95%B4%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"주의사항 및 적용 해제하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>주의사항 및 적용 해제하기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"주의-사항\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98-%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\" aria-label=\"주의 사항 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>주의 사항</h3>\n<p>만약 프로젝트를 레포지토리에서 새로 clone 한 경우 터미널에 <code class=\"language-text\">make</code>를 입력해야 스크립트가 적용됩니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"적용-해제하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9-%ED%95%B4%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"적용 해제하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>적용 해제하기</h3>\n<p>적용을 해제하려면 터미널에 <code class=\"language-text\">git config core.hooksPath .git/hooks</code>를 입력해서 원래 설정으로 돌려놓으면 됩니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"마치며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EC%B9%98%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\"마치며 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>마치며</h2>\n<p>해당 글에서는 적용 방법에 대한 내용만 작성했습니다.</p>\n<p>만약 각 과정의 이유에 대해 알아보고 싶은 분들은 <a href=\"https://blog.deercorp.com/commit-convention/\">해당 포스팅</a>을 참고해주세요.</p>\n<h3 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16